  "player join world": "§2-%s-§fArriving at the Shanhai Continent - The Shanhai Continent: At the beginning of the universe, chaotic evolution, the energy of creation, the creation of all things, the power of mountains, rivers, and seas, and the birth of all things",
  "《万破》：每10级增加10%的物攻": "Ten Thousand Breaks: Increases physical attacks by 10% every 10 levels",
  "一株草可斩日月星辰!挑出一剑，对前方大范围敌人伤害": "A single blade of grass can slay the sun, moon, and stars! Pick out a sword and deal damage to a wide range of enemies ahead",
  "上古神王附体": "thePossessionOfTheAncientDivineKing",
  "不能突破": "§cUnable to break through: Please absorb the soul ring first",
  "以自身为中心，形成一个魂力漩涡，对5格范围内的敌人造成伤害": "Form a soul vortex centered around oneself, dealing damage to enemies within a 5-grid range",
  "以造化之气，炼制物品": "refiningObjectsWithTheEnergyOfNature",
  "体力": "physicalStrength：%s/%s",
  "击杀《古风小屋》中的魂民概率掉落": "Probability of Killing Soul People in 'Ancient Wind House' Dropping",
  "分出三根破天神棍，对前方造成伤害": "Separate three Heavenly God Breaking Staff and deal damage to the front",
  "刷新所有技能冷却": "refreshAllSkillCooldowns",
  "发出强大的力量风暴，前方的敌人造成伤害": "Send out a powerful storm of force, causing damage to enemies ahead",
  "受到致命伤满血复活": "resurrectedFromFatalInjuriesAndFullOfBlood",
  "召唤雷电轰击地面": "summonLightningToStrikeTheGround",
  "可通过造化炉修理": "canBeRepairedThroughAChemicalFurnace",
  "右键<魂核>收集能量；右键<耕地>消耗能量，转化<魂土>": "Right click on<Soul Core>to collect energy; Right click on<Farmland>to consume energy and convert<Soul Soil>",
  "向前位移，对路过的敌人造成伤害": "moveForwardAndDealDamageToPassingEnemies",
